{"lemma":"طُرُقُ","slug":"طُرُقُ","root":"ط.ر.ق","root_slug":"ط-ر-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-ر-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"طَرِيق","root":"طرق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":4},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26643","n26651","n26652","n26653","n26654"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%8F%D9%82%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"way, road, path, track, street"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ط ر ق (ṭ r q). Possibly related to Hebrew דֶּרֶךְ (dérekh, “road”)."},"ipa":["/tˤa.riːq/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26643","headword_ar":"طَرْقٌ","root":"Trq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beating"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a thing], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"striking"},{"kind":"text","text":"[it, in any manner, and with anything]; (K, TA;) this being the primary meaning: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miToraqap","text_ar":"مِطْرَقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) which is the implement of the blacksmith and of the artificer [with which he beats the iron], and the rod, or stick, with which one beats wool [or hair] to loosen or separate it: (TA:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slapping"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) with the hand. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqa AlbaAba","text_ar":"طَرَقَ البَابَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He knocked"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or (as we say)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"knocked at"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the door."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqa AlS~uwfa","text_ar":"طَرَقَ الصُّوفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, TA, *) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~aEara","text_ar":"الشَّعَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) aor. as above, (S, O,) and so the inf. n., (S, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He beat the wool,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the hair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the rod,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stick, called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miToraqap","text_ar":"مِطْرَقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to loosen it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"separate it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * O, * TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he plucked it"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to loosen it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"separate it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K, TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AuToruqiY","text_ar":"اُطْرُقِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wamiy$iY","text_ar":"وَمِيشِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", a prov., and occurring in a verse of Ru-beh, [originally addressed to a woman,] and [lit.] meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Beat thou the wool with the stick, and mix the hair with the wool,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to him who confuses or confounds, in his speech, and practises various modes, or manners, therein. (Az, TA. [See Freytag's Arab. Prov. ii. 28.]) And you say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqa AlHadiydapa","text_ar":"طَرَقَ الحَدِيدَةَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He beat the piece of iron"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miToraqap","text_ar":"مِطْرَقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Mgh, * Msb:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tr~qhA","text_ar":"طرّقها","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he beat it much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemently."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqahu bikaf~ihi","text_ar":"طَرَقَهُ بِكَفِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He slapped him with his hand."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqotu","text_ar":"طَرَقْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~ariyqa","text_ar":"الطَّرِيقَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I travelled"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beat"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the road."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [And hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being quick of pace;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[probably as an inf. n.;] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quickness of going along."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Turiqati AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"طُرِقَتِ الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ground was beaten so as to be rendered even,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy to be travelled;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trodden with the feet."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqa Ald~awaAb~u AlmaA='a biAlr~ijoli Hat~aY tukad~irahu","text_ar":"طَرَقَ الدَّوَابُّ المَا=ءَ بِالرِّجْلِ حَتَّى تُكَدِّرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The beasts beat the water with the foot so as to render it turbid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"muddy"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Er-Rághib, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqati AlA_ibilu AlmaA='a","text_ar":"طَرَقَتِ الاـِبِلُ المَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, TA,) aor. as above, (O,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the camels staled and dunged in the water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coming by night;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) because he who comes by night [generally] needs to knock at the door; as some say; (TA;) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuruwqN","text_ar":"طُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is the more common in this sense]. (K, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqa","text_ar":"طَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuruwqN","text_ar":"طُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came by night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataAnaA fulaAnN TuruwqFA","text_ar":"اَتَانَا فُلَانٌ طُرُوقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one came to us by night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqa Alqawoma","text_ar":"طَرَقَ القَوْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuruwqN","text_ar":"طُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came to the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, by night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqa A^aholahu","text_ar":"طَرَقَ اَهْلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqa A^aholahu layolFA","text_ar":"طَرَقَ اَهْلَهُ لَيْلًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuruwqN","text_ar":"طُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came to his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ahl","text_ar":"اهل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wife"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * O, TA:) the doing of which by him who has been long absent is forbidden by the Prophet. (O, TA. *) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqa Aln~ajomu","text_ar":"طَرَقَ النَّجْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuruwqN","text_ar":"طُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The star,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asterism, rose:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and of anything that has come by night, one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqa","text_ar":"طَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Turiqa fulaAnN","text_ar":"طُرِقَ فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one was made an object of"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was visited by"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was smitten by"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nocturnal accidents"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"calamities."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqahu Alz~amaAnu","text_ar":"طَرَقَهُ الزَّمَانُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"binawaAy^ibihi","text_ar":"بِنَوَايِبِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fortune, visited him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smote him, with its accidents,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"calamities;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did so suddenly, like one knocking at the door in the night"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqaniY xayaAlN","text_ar":"طَرَقَنِى خَيَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An apparition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a phantom, visited me in the night"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqaniY ham~N","text_ar":"طَرَقَنِى هَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Anxiety came upon me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did so suddenly, like one coming in the night"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And [hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqa samoEiY","text_ar":"طَرَقَ سَمْعِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka*aA","text_ar":"كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a thing struck my ear"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Turiqato","text_ar":"طُرِقَتْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masaAmiEiY bixayorK","text_ar":"مَسَامِعِى بِخَيْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"My ears were struck by good tidings"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  Also The stallion's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covering"},{"kind":"text","text":"the she-camel; (Msb, K; *) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuruwqN","text_ar":"طُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiraAqN","text_ar":"طِرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"likewise [app. another inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqa","text_ar":"طَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as its syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DiraAbN","text_ar":"ضِرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daraba","text_ar":"ضَرَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) or his"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leaping"},{"kind":"text","text":"her, (S, O, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and covering"},{"kind":"text","text":"her. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqa AlqaHolu Aln~aAqapa","text_ar":"طَرَقَ القَحْلُ النَّاقَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuruwqN","text_ar":"طُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S) or both, (O, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The stallion covered the she-camel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leaped the she-camel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and covered her."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  And [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"practising of pessomancy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DarobN biAlHaSaY","text_ar":"ضَرْبٌ بِالحَصَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, IAth, O, K,) which is performed by women, (IAth, TA,) or by a diviner; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain mode of divination:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or [the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"practising of geomancy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.] a man's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making lines,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"marks, upon the ground, with two fingers, and then with one finger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AibonaYo EiyaAno A^asoriEaA AlbayaAno","text_ar":"اِبْنَىْ عِيَانْ اَسْرِعَا البَيَانْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (AZ, O, TA: [see this saying explained, with another description of the process, in the first paragraph of art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xT","text_ar":"خط"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) or it is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making lines,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"marks, upon the sand:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taraqa","text_ar":"طَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made lines,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"marks, with a finger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(&c.,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in divining."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.) [See the last sentence in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jbt","text_ar":"جبت"},{"kind":"text","text":".] Also The diviner's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mixing cotton with wool when divining."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, K.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqonaA Aln~aEojapa","text_ar":"طَرَقْنَا النَّعْجَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We branded the ewe with the mark called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiraAq","text_ar":"طِرَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":". (ISh, O.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Turiqa","text_ar":"طُرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuniYa","text_ar":"عُنِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) [inf. n., app.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.,] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, weak in intellect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and soft."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tariqa","text_ar":"طَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqN","text_ar":"طَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, S, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had a weakness in his knees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, S, O, K: [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalalN","text_ar":"حَلَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) or, said of a human being and of a camel,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had a weakness in the knee and in the arm"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the fore leg:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or, said of a camel,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had a crookedness in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAq","text_ar":"سَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, * O, * K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the kind leg,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the thigh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of straddling termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHaj","text_ar":"فَحَج"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and with an inclining in the heel."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O.) ―         -b2-  [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqN","text_ar":"طَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below.]       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tariqa","text_ar":"طَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drank turbid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"muddy, water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maToruwqN","text_ar":"مَطْرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA. [In the K it is said to be, in this sense, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samiEa","text_ar":"سَمِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; which seems to indicate that the inf. n. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqN","text_ar":"طَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":["TA","K","S","O","Msb","IAth","Fr"]},{"entry_id":"n26651","headword_ar":"طَرْقٌ","root":"Trq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[originally an inf. n., and as such app. signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An act of striking"},{"kind":"text","text":"the lute &c.: and hence,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a species"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DarobN","text_ar":"ضَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSowaAt","text_ar":"اَصْوَات"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sounds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"airs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tunes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the lute:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sawot","text_ar":"صَوْت"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"air,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tune"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Lth, O, K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nagomap","text_ar":"نَغْمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"melody"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the lute"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, by itself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O, K, TA:) you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taDoribu h`*ihi AljaAriyapu ka*aA waka*aA TaroqFA","text_ar":"تَضْرِبُ هٰذِهِ الجَارِيَةُ كَذَا وَكَذَا طَرْقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This girl,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young woman,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"female slave, plays such and such airs"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tunes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such and such melodies, of the lute"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Lth, O, K. *) ―         -b2-  [Hence, probably,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Einodahu TuruwqN mina AlkalaAmi","text_ar":"عِنْدَهُ طُرُوقٌ مِنَ الكَلَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", sing."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a phrase mentioned by Kr; thought by ISd to mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"various"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sorts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"species, of speech."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqapN","text_ar":"طَرْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places.       -A2-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A stallion"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covering:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuruwqN","text_ar":"طُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tur~aAqN","text_ar":"طُرَّاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) an inf. n. used as a subst. [or an epithet]: (O, K, TA:) for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw TaroqK","text_ar":"ذُو طَرْقٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  And (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sperma"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the stallion [camel]: (S, K:) a man says to another,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEironiY","text_ar":"اَعِرْنِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taroqa faHolika AlEaAma","text_ar":"طَرْقَ فَحْلِكَ العَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Lend thou to me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sperma,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the covering,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, TA.) which latter is said to be the original meaning, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of thy stallion"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camel this year"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (As, TA.) And it is said to be sometimes applied metaphorically to (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sperma"},{"kind":"text","text":"of man: or in relation to man, it may be an epithet, [like as it is sometimes in relation to a stallion-camel, as mentioned above,] and not"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1848},{"kind":"text","text":"metaphorical. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taroqu Aljamali","text_ar":"طَرْقُ الجَمَلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The hire that is given for the camel's covering of the female."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$br","text_ar":"شبر"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A3-  Also, and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maToruwqN","text_ar":"مَطْرُوقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Water"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the rain"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which camels"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and others"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other beasts"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have staled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waded and staled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * O, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and dunged:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stagnant water in which beasts have waded and staled:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqN","text_ar":"طَرَقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[expressly stated to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHar~akap","text_ar":"مُحَرَّكَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"] signifies [the same, or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water that has collected, in which there has been a wading and staling, so that it has become turbid;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"places where water collects and stagnates"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in stony tracts of land;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) and the pl. of this is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aToraAqN","text_ar":"اَطْرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"snare, trap, gin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"net, such as is commonly called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fax~","text_ar":"فَخّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAar, O, K,) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiroqN","text_ar":"طِرْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K: [by Golius and Freytag, this meaning has been assigned to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqapN","text_ar":"طَرْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and by Freytag, to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiroqapN","text_ar":"طِرْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also; in consequence of a want of clearness in the K:]) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a snare,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing by means of which wild animals are taken,"},{"kind":"text","text":"like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fax~","text_ar":"فَخّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Lth, O;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqapN","text_ar":"طَرَقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) of which the pl. [or coll. gen. n.] is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqN","text_ar":"طَرَقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) signifies [the same, or] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"snare"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HibaAlap","text_ar":"حِبَالَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sportsman,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what are termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kifaf","text_ar":"كِفَف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kif~apN","text_ar":"كِفَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]. (S, O)       -A5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A palm-tree:"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the dial. of Teiyi. (AHn, K.)       -A6-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Weakness of intellect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and softness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Turiqa","text_ar":"طُرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":["TA","Lth","O","K","S","Mgh","IAar"]},{"entry_id":"n26652","headword_ar":"طُرْقٌ","root":"Trq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqapN","text_ar":"طَرْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  [Also a contraction of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuruqN","text_ar":"طُرُقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TariyqN","text_ar":"طَرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]       -A3-  And pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiraAqN","text_ar":"طِرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n26653","headword_ar":"طِرْقٌ","root":"Trq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as a subst.: (S, O, K:) this is the primary signification. (S, O.) [See an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bin~N","text_ar":"بِنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fatness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA AlbaEiyru maA bih TiroqN","text_ar":"هٰذَا البَعِيرُ مَا بِه طِرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This camel has not in him fatness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, TA.) It is said to be mostly used in negative phrases. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Strength:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) because it mostly arises from fat. (S, O.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA bihi TiroqN","text_ar":"مَا بِهِ طِرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not in him strength."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) The pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aToraAqN","text_ar":"اَطْرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last quarter."}],"source_refs":["S","O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n26654","headword_ar":"طَرَقٌ","root":"Trq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", third quarter. ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu*al~alN","text_ar":"مُذَلَّلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[applied to a beast, app. to a camel,] meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rendered submissive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tractable;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broken."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  It is also pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqapN","text_ar":"طَرَقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or rather is a coll. gen. n. of which the n. un. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqapN","text_ar":"طَرَقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (S, O, K,) which latter signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A row"},{"kind":"text","text":"of bricks in a wall, or of other things, (S, O,) or [particularly] of palm-trees. (As, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also, ↓ the latter, [as is expressly stated in the TA, and indicated in the S and O, ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=vAru","text_ar":"ا=ثارُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEoDuhaA","text_ar":"بَعْضُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the CK being mistakes for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=vAri","text_ar":"ا=ثارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEoDihaA","text_ar":"بَعْضِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":",)] The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foot-marks"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"track"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of camels following near after one another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAHidapK","text_ar":"وَاحِدَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='ati AlA_ibilu EalaY TaraqapK","text_ar":"جَا=ءَتِ الاـِبِلُ عَلَى طَرَقَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camels came upon one track"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in one line"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; like as you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY xuf~K waAHidK","text_ar":"عَلَى خُفٍّ وَاحِدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O. [See also a similar phrase voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miToraAqN","text_ar":"مِطْرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And Aboo-Turáb mentions, as a phrase of certain of BenooKiláb,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_ibili","text_ar":"الاـِبِلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mararotu EalaY Taraqapi","text_ar":"مَرَرْتُ عَلَى طَرَقَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaraqatihaA","text_ar":"عَرَقَتِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I went upon the track of the camels."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last quarter.       -A3-  Also, i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqN","text_ar":"طَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A duplicature,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fold,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vinoY","text_ar":"ثِنْى"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the CK [erroneously]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vanoY","text_ar":"ثَنْى"},{"kind":"text","text":",) of a water-skin: (S, O, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aToraAqN","text_ar":"اَطْرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is its pl., (S, O,) signifying its"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"duplicatures,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"folds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when it is bent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when it is doubled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"folded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and bent."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aToraAqu AlbaToni","text_ar":"اَطْرَاقُ البَطْنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The parts of the belly that lie one above another"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when it is wrinkled:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqN","text_ar":"طَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqN","text_ar":"طَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the feathers of a bird is their"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Overlying one another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA:) or, accord. to the A, it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"softness and flaccidity"},{"kind":"text","text":"therein. (TA.) ―         -b4-  [Also inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tariqa","text_ar":"طَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA"]}]}}